messages.content: Decided to make a quick stop at Dominus' room to tell her the good news, Meriad gently knocked on her door and waited
There was a muffled, “Come in.....”
Meriad opened the door "Hi Domi....!" She smiled "I got my voice back..."
“Oh! That’s......wonderful Meriad.....” She seemed exhausted, slumped on her desk, there’s was too many dirty mugs on it to count.
"Tired...? Why dont you sleep..." she tilted her head
“Nono.....it just......do you think I’m a bad person?” Dominus looked up at her. “Honest.”
She shook her head "No! Not at all!!!!" She walked over and cupped the others cheeks "You are an amazing person. No if ands or buts about it. Whats makes you think youre a bad person?"

“I-I just.....I’m afraid.....to fight.....because even though those other muns or plasma are on the opposing side i-I *still see them as precious, unique beings that should be proteced*......I only used my electric abilities to harm a mun once.....even then it was in defense of another mun but I still felt terrible!” Her voice was incredibly shaky as she sobbed Into Meriads hands, “And I don’t know how much longer I can keep up this facade for the kids....” she sniffed, “Maybe Quartz was right....”
"Shh....Its ok....Its ok...You dont have to fight..." She held her close, kissing her head.
“I w-want this whole revolution thing to be over......I-I don’t want them to see me as a v-villain....”
"I hope it will be over soon...I dont think they see you as a villain....They are just....scared....." She gently kissed her forehead

Meriad picked her up and brought her to the bed, laying with her. "How about we cuddle for a bit....Maybe it can help you feel better...? Even if its only a tiny bit, seeing you happy in any way is good..." She purred
She began to hum a little, hoping it would help
She silently snuggled into Meriads neck, hiccuping s few times.
She ran a hand through her hair, humming still and doing her best to help her feel better
“Thank you......Meriad.”
"No problem Domi....I wanna make you happy after all...." She smiled
She gave a small smile back, cuddling as the plasma calmed down
She placed a kiss on her forehead again, tail wagging a bit "You're so pretty.....One of the many reasons I love you...."
“You’re prettier.”
"No you are." She giggled
Meriad yawned a bit, cuddling her more "I love you so much....."
She smiled, cheekily doing a little ‘pphblt’. Her little fin ears waggling.
((**ITS A FUCKING EPIDEMY**
((AAAAAA))
(PLAGUE)
(PLAGUE PLAGUE PLAGUE)
(Huh)
She giggled at that, her own ear fins wiggling
“Bet I can wiggle mine faster”
"Oh really???" She grinned more, tail wagging
Meriad looked back at the door. "....Did.....you hear that???"
“Yeah....” she looked concerned
"We should go check it out..." She got up and picked Dominus uo with ease "Im gonna carry you because I wanna~"
“Oh!” She gasped, “Well.....this is welcomed..”
She giggled, kissing her cheek
Meriad knocks on the door "Domi? You ready?"
The door slowly squeaks open, Dominus having a giddy smile
She smiled "Hi~ Im excited...I assume you are as well? Decorations are done, Cakes done, Rings have been made, All thats left is to check if everyone else is ready!"
“Mhm!”
She offered a hand out to her "Come on!"
She gave it a little squeeze, standing up, “weddings always bring a tear to my eye.”
"This is my first wedding Ive ever attended....Im excited." She smiled befire leading her to check on the others
(Im gonna assume we are here now
Dominus gently placed Meriad on her bed
Meriad is whimpering and holding her stomach in pain.
“Do you want me to get anything for you darling?” She fretted
She shook her head, looking up at her
“Alright...I’m staying here with you until you feel better...” she sighed siting next to her
Meriad held her hand "I-I....domt think....I can eat....anything other....then meat....." She whimpered
“What *did* you eat?”
"Waffles....." She sits up "M-Met another Plasma named Somnus....Sh-She took me to a waffle house...."
(ha cha cha)
(Jshevdieheie)
“I’ve never trusted those low quality restaurants.....and I’m not crossing out this Somuns as a explanation for this sickness either.”
"I only....ever ate meat before..." She sighed "I-I domt think my body likes me eating....non meat stuff.......Can.....you get a bucket or a trashcan please...."
“Oh yes....” she positioned the can from the corner of the room near Meriad
She took it and ||threw up|| into it.
She wiped her mouth afterwards, sighing a bit.
She moved closer to Dominus, hugging her

She rubbed soothing circles down Meriads back
“There, there...”
Her tail wagged a bit, a small purring raising in her throat
"Mmm....I love you...." She purred
"...Do you....think you could help me...test my theory later...? Make something that....doesnt have meat in it...I wanna see if....thats the reason im not feeling well..."

She bites her lip 
“I don’t know......I don’t want you getting sick again..,”
"Its only for the best...Its to make sure I know what to no eat....." She hummed
Her stomach grumbles a bit, making her blush out of embarrassment

Dominus goggled
“We have leftover burgers in the fridge.”
"Thank you...." She tried to stand but fell flat on her face. "...."
“I’ll get it for you.”
She crawled back into bed "Thank you Domi..."

Arándano rushed over to the 2 guards outside of Dominus' room. She took a moment to catch her breath before speaking "Veteris, Sanguis, A large fox crashed in through the window and I have no idea what it wants but I dont think its friendly!"
“Ah fuck!” Veteris Already had his giant blade drawn “where is it??”
"I-I think it ran off to the kitchen!"
"I luckily was able to get Aion to her room and out of harms way...Ill clean the glass up after the fox is taken care of...."
